Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing dramatic is guaranteed to happen\Njust because it's Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.84,0:00:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's not going to be\Na great memory or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.96,0:00:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly is Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.75,0:00:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how grand is this phenomenon\Nknown as Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.13,0:00:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a right way to celebrate Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this luck that supposedly\Ncomes with Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.21,0:00:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Does something that's born\Non Christmas shine bright?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Good Luck"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly are you\Nsupposed to do on Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly are you\Nsupposed to do on Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.63,0:00:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit spacing out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.88,0:00:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. U-Um, Manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.71,0:00:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,May I take Christmas...\NMay I take the 25th off?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.96,0:01:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I wouldn't exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...call it that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,First off, is a date where you do
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.38,0:02:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,something fun with someone you're\Ninterested in to get closer to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And in that case, I guess you could\Nsort of call this a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My date with Shimamura...\NWhat should we do on Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Chicken, a cake, a tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,a present...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A present for Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A present, a present...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A Christmas present for Shimamura--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Heya, Adachicchi! What're you spaced out for?\NYou feeling faint?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you must be waiting for Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's rare to see you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wut?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.05,0:03:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. She's not here.\NHow did she lose me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you need to wait for Nagafuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't usually get the chance\Nto ask you out to lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the grub!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what Shimamura likes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she have anything she actually likes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not the type of person that\Nactually talks about stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been shopping with Shimamura before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have, but it's usually like a bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and we've peeked in a tea shop before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tea shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we went because of me,\Nbut Shimamura did have a look, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I think there was a certain tea\Nthat she said smelled good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't remember if it\Nwas black tea or green...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't happen to remember\Nthe name of that tea, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... One sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, what was it? It wasn't barley tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Which shelf was it on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The name is on the tip of my tongue, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I can remember it if I see it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you see it... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you look for it with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. I mean, you could just\Ntake Shimamura with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll go with you and choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's Hino!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are.\NWhere'd you get lost at, Nagafuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you shrink?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.50,0:05:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just you seem smaller than usual,\Nso I lost track of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,--What'd you say?!\N--Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind if I have some ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over some bread, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,--There's a sweet one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,--They're so close...\N--There's a sweet one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,--They're so close...\N--Ooh, give me that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'd ever... be able to smack\NShimamura on the head like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Adatty, have you been waiting long?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagafuji's not with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She apparently had something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a day like that like\Nonce a year. Anyway, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Do you want to get on the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I will, but we should\Nget away from school first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If a teacher sees us,\Nwe'll never hear the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought of you as an honor student.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Praise me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet it is pretty weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That I'm imagining walking around town\Non Christmas with another girl
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:06:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and my heart is about to burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that Shimamura isn't\Nthis anxious about Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's definitely a difference in how\NI feel about Shimamura and vice versa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not sure if I want her\Nto realize that... or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Jikkokuya Jyugoro"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Jikkokuya Jyugoro"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming by again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Jikkokuya Jyugoro"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Heya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Ginger Tea"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Ginger Tea"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I may or may not have someone\Nin my family who drinks a lot of tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginger... That'd probably warm you right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, it works great\Nfor people who get cold easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,According to my family member.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't drink it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't exactly get cold easily.\NLet's see, where was it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure it was on this shelf...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Adatty. Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the type that would get mad\Nif I confidently told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Yeah, this is the one!" and was totally wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think my personality sucks that badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good. Then I think it's this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Man... Thanks for treating me.\NThough I sorta talked you into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit chilly in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My legs are freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're totally anxious because you\Ndon't know what to say right now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it would've been the same\Nwith Nagafuji here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, in her case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what she had to do...\NDid you know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief. What am I going to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna follow them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not. They seem busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Adatty, always the honor student.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was the only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...that got to hang out\Nwith Shimamura alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Why were you with Nagafuji?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...that got to hang out\Nwith Shimamura alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And the fact that I was totally wrong\Nabout that shouldn't hurt this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just saying her name...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.34,0:10:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the sound of her name was enough\Nto get me through this winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.84,0:10:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really an alien, Yachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk, tsk, tsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course. I have never told a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.75,0:10:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Then show me proof!\NProof that you're an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk, tsk, tsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be violating my agreement\Nif I showed you, so I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The rules of the universe\Ncan be rather strict. Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that, Little Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.92,0:10:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my, my, what a dramatic sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one that's dramatic, Yachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just breathe into it more gently...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's almost discount time, so I must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Alienspeak?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura and I are just normal friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, that's how Shimamura sees us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even then, I still want to get\Ncloser to Shimamura one step at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm looking forward to tomorrow."\NEven then, I still want to get\Ncloser to Shimamura one step at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm looking forward to tomorrow."\NBut the closer you get,\Nthe more things get across.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But the closer you get,\Nthe more things get across.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep mentioning Christmas\Nwith Shimamura, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it love? No, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Romance? No, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Like...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it is, it's warm and fuzzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a warm liquid that flows through my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"Cool!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Cool!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this "Cool" supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, "Coolio"? Maybe she meant, "Chill out"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, "Cool beans"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Cool!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear Shimamura's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know more about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll be able to hear\Nand ask her lots tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you waiting long?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been watching you sitting here\Nfor the last five minutes from afar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, I was just joking. Anyway,\Nsorry for making you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I've been wondering\Never since I saw you today...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you wearing your Chinese dress\Nfrom work under your coat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh... Yeah, I guess I can't\Nblame you for wondering.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,won't people think you're trying\Nto lure them into a sketchy shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, even I know this is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But... She said I looked cute in it, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I think it's fine. You look super cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be nice being so pretty.\NYou can actually pull that outfit off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But you're even cuter Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can skip the sarcasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,--Christmas all alone with Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,--So, where are you taking me today?\N--Christmas all alone with Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,--Um, we should go to the 2nd floor.\N--Though Shimamura's probably only here\Nbecause she felt obligated as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,--Though Shimamura's probably only here\Nbecause she felt obligated as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to stop. Whenever I let my guard down,\Nmy thoughts just go down a dark path
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll get depressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, really. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't suddenly grab my hand\Nlike a purse-snatcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want to hold hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.67,0:14:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:15:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we do this all before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Possibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.50,0:15:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, make sure you just ask if it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.09,0:15:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of response is that?\NHow did you even pronounce that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You might've sounded like a shrimp just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.42,0:15:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just ignore that. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it, though. I'll ask next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to panic so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No one else is going to steal my hand from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not the only one\Nthat gets to walk next to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:15:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking we could play here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... An arcade.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey. A ping-pong table.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We could play... this. Air hockey.\NWhat do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Air hockey is sort of similar\Nto ping-pong in some ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,--This was our pastime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,--You can go first, Adachi.\N--This was our pastime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,--Okay, take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,--Okay, take that!\N--Shimamura and I met\Non the second floor of the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how it happened, once we've met,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a path that\Nled us there as well as fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--No matter the encounter, there's always\Na grand past that goes along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,--This is sorta different.\N--No matter the encounter, there's always\Na grand past that goes along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,--What do you mean?\N--No matter the encounter, there's always\Na grand past that goes along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.09,0:16:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--I play the video game version\Nof this at home with my sister,\N--Two hundred, 500, billions of\Nactions done by everyone and everything
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,--and it's definitely a bit different.\N--Two hundred, 500, billions of\Nactions done by everyone and everything
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,piled up together in order\Nfor two people to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of paths led us to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Even one different decision would've meant\Nthat I wouldn't have met Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And that fact alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Made me endlessly like my past self.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're pretty good at this, Adachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.25,0:17:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How you like them apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, Adachi. You're super good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected you to be\Nthe type to pick on noobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you also had more wins\Nin ping-pong, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, maybe it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fair to make stuff up\Njust because I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't seem that long ago somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,When spring comes and we become second-years\Nand the sun is out more again,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.13,0:17:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if we're gonna go to the gym again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:18:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we can just go to class,\Ncome here after school, and play ping-pong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A perfect score. You're a total\Nhonor student now, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But man, we're gonna be second-years...\NWe'll probably be in different classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.71,0:18:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura... here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought you a Christmas gift... or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.17,0:18:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... Well, this was a nice surprise.\NCan I open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey. This is the nice smelling one.\NI wanted to try it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But how did you know I liked this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.21,0:18:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... Oh, you must've asked Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You really didn't have to, Adachi.\NBut thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:19:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd be\Nthinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're such a good little girl, Adachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.59,0:19:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis got you a present, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A boomerang... Oh, and some goggles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I supposed to wear it\Nwhen I throw this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Oh, I threw it\Na few times before buying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's way more fun than you'd expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I suck at choosing stuff like this,\Nso I asked Nagafuji to help me pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she'd want a boomerang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I think kids would love them. They're super fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.09,0:19:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Though they tend to snap when you\Nthrow them around in winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just told Nagafuji I was getting\Na present for my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagafuji... I see.\NSo that's why she was with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks... I'll take really good care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I didn't care\Nabout the boomerang, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that Shimamura gave this to me...\Nwas the best gift I could ask for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yeah. You hold the boomerang behind you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and then throw it in front of you like you're\Ngoing to chop something vertically.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like that. Make sure you\Ndon't throw it up, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.34,0:20:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's your first try.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you able to catch it, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.17,0:21:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But that's not bad for a beginner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But you sorta look like you're in some movie,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,throwing that thing in your Chinese dress.\NIt's very cinematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.46,0:21:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Not feeling it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.25,0:21:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.21,0:21:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Hey, should I go back\Nand buy you something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.55,0:21:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. I really like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.42,0:21:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But we probably should head back.\NIt's warmer inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This was my only chance, I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.84,0:21:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, where no one else was around...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.67,0:21:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the only place I'd be able to say\Nsomething like this to Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:22:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.84,0:22:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm not ready...\NEven if I fall on my face...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.63,0:22:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.59,0:22:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.92,0:22:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.34,0:22:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like you, Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, really like you... love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.96,0:22:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.42,0:22:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...want to be your friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.63,0:22:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure we already are?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.05,0:22:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not just friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.67,0:22:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to be like, your best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.71,0:22:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My best friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.30,0:23:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I sorta really want to be that, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.50,0:23:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.30,0:23:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.34,0:23:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's great that you're so ambitious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.46,0:23:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.34,0:23:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing dramatic is guaranteed to happen\Njust because it's Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.00,0:23:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's not going to be\Na great memory or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.09,0:23:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, my mind just kept going blank,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so I didn't really have a chance\Nto remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.75,0:23:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like scenery being covered in snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.92,0:23:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to carve the memory of\Na white album into the back of my brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.05,0:23:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 6: 'White Album'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.05,0:23:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to carve the memory of\Na white album into the back of my brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.42,0:23:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 6: 'White Album'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.00,0:23:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time:\N'Please Choose the Best Chocolate for Me'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.88,0:23:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time:\N'Please Choose the Best Chocolate for Me'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.88,0:23:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Adashimapedia: Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.30,0:23:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,--What are you mad about, Hino?\N--I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.42,0:23:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some chicken curry\Nat my place on Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.67,0:24:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Christmas, so chicken curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.38,0:24:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. It's a Nagafuji family tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.30,0:24:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Guess I'll just have to come over then!
